quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  27,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  27,1,toy seen yeh ayaat hain quran aur kitaab Mubin ki
  27,2,hadaayat aur basharat unn imaan laane walon ke liye
  27,3,"jo namaz qaim karte aur zkoh dete hain, aur phir woh aisay log hain jo akhirat par poora yaqeen rakhtay hain"
  27,4,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log akhirat ko nahi mantay un ke liye hum ne unn ke krtoton ko khushnuma bana diya hai, is liye woh bhataktay phir rahay hain"
  27,5,yeh woh log hain jin ke liye burii saza hai aur akhirat mein yahi sab se ziyada khasaray mein rehne walay hain
  27,6,aur ( aeMuhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) bilashuba tum yeh quran aik hakeem o Aleem hasti ki taraf se pa rahay ho
  27,7,"( aِnhin uss waqt ka qissa sunaaoo ) jab moose ne apne ghar walon se kaha ke"" mujhe aik aag si nazar aayi hai, mein abhi ya to wahan se koi khabar le kar aata hon ya koi angara chunn lata hon taakay tum log garam ho sakuu """
  27,8,"wahan jo pouncha to nida aayi ke"" mubarak hai woh jo is aag mein hai aur jo is ke mahol mein hai pak hai Allah , sab jahanon ka parvar-digaar"
  27,9,"ae moose, yeh mein hon Allah , zabardast aur Dana"
  27,10,"aur pheink to zara apni laathi"" jounhi ke moose ne dekha laathi saanp ki terhan bil kha rahi hai to peeth phair kar bhaga aur peechay murr kar bhi nah dekha"" ae moose, daro nahi mere huzoor rasool dara nahi karte"
  27,11,ila yeh ke kisi ne qasoor kya ho phir agar buraiee ke baad uss ne BHALAI se apne fael ko badal liya to mein maaf karne wala meharban hon
  27,12,"aur zara apna haath apne garibaan mein to daalo chamakta howa niklay ga baghair kisi takleef ke yeh ( do nishanain ) no nishanion mein se hain firaon aur is ki qoum ki taraf ( le jaane ke liye ), woh barray bad kirdaar log hain """
  27,13,magar jab hamari khuli khuli nishanain unn logon ke samnay ayen to unhon ne kaha yeh to khula jaadoo hai
  27,14,unhon ne sara sar zulm aur ghuroor ki raah se un nishanion ka inkaar kya halaank dil un ke qaail ho chuke thay ab dekh lau ke un mfsdon ka injaam kaisa howa
  27,15,( doosri taraf ) hum ne DAWOD o sulaiman ko ilm ataa kya aur unhon ne kaha ke shukar hai uss khuda ka jis ne hum ko apne bohat se momin bundon par fazeelat ataa ki
  27,16,"aur DAWOD ka waris sulaiman howa aur is ne kaha"" “logo, hamein parindon ki buliyan sikhayi gayi hain aur hamein har terhan ki cheeze di gayi hain, bay shak yeh ( Allah ka ) numaya fazl hai """
  27,17,sulaiman ke liye jin aur insanon aur parindon ke lashkar jama kiye gay thay aur woh poooray zabt mein rakhay jatay thay
  27,18,"( aik martaba woh un ke sath coach kar raha tha ) yahan taq ke jab yeh sab chyontyon ki waadi mein puhanche to aik choonti ne kaha"" “ay chuntiyo, apne bilon mein ghis jao, kahin aisa nah ho ke sulaiman aur is ke lashkar tumhe kuchal dalain aur inhen khabar bhi nah ho """
  27,19,"sulaiman is ki baat par Muskuratay hue hans para aur bola"" ae mere rab, mujhe qaboo mein rakh ke mein tairay is ahsaan ka shukar ada karta rahon jo to ne mujh par aur mere walidain par kya hai aur aisa amal Saleh karoon jo tujhe pasand aeye aur apni rehmat se mujh ko apne Saleh bundon mein daakhil kar """
  27,20,( aik aur mauqa par ) sulaiman ne parindon ka jaiza liya aur kaha “کیا baat hai ke mein falan hُd hُd ko nahi dekh raha hon kya woh kahin gayab ho gaya hai ?
  27,21,"mein usay sakht saza dun ga, ya zibah kar dun ga, warna usay mere samnay maqool wajah paish karni ho gi"
  27,22,"kuch ziyada der nah guzri thi ke uss ne aa kar kaha"" “min ne woh maloomat haasil ki hain jo aap ke ilm mein nahi hain mein saba ke mutaliq yakeeni ittila le kar aaya hon"
  27,23,mein ne wahan aik aurat dekhi jo is qoum ki hukmaran hai uss ko har terhan ka saaz o samaan bakhsha gaya hai aur is ka takhat bara azeem al shan hai
  27,24,"mein ne dekha hai ke woh aur is ki qoum Allah ke bajaye Sooraj ke agay sajda karti hai"" shetan ne un ke aamaal un ke liye khushnuma bana diye aur inhen shahrah se rok diya, is wajah se woh yeh seedha rasta nahi paate"
  27,25,ke uss khuda ko sajda karen jo asmano aur zameen ki posheeda cheeze nikalta hai aur woh sab kuch jaanta hai jisay tum log chupatay ho aur zahir karte ho
  27,26,"Allah ke jis ke siwa koi mustahiq ibadat nahi, jo arsh azeem ka maalik hai"
  27,27,"sulaiman ne kaha"" abhi hum dekhe letay hain ke to ne sach kaha hai ya to jhoot bolnay walon mein se hai"
  27,28,"mera yeh khat le ja aur usay un logon ki taraf daal day, phir allag hatt kar dekh ke woh kya radd amal zahir karte hain """
  27,29,"malka boli"" ae ehley darbaar, meri taraf aik bara ahem khat phenka gaya hai"
  27,30,woh sulaiman ki janib se hai aur Allah rehman o Raheem ke naam se shuru kya gaya hai
  27,31,"mazmoon yeh hai ke “meraymuqablay mein sar kashi nah karo aur muslim ho kar mere paas haazir ho jao """
  27,32,"( khat suna kar ) malka ne kaha"" “ay sardaran qoum mere is muamlay mein mujhe mahswara do, mein kisi maamla ka faisla tumahray baghair nahi karti hon """
  27,33,"onhon ne jawab diya"" hum taaqat war aur larnay walay log hain agay faisla aap ke haath mein hai aap khud dekh len ke aap ko kya hukum dena hai """
  27,34,"malka ne kaha ke"" badshah jab kisi mulk mein ghis atay hain to usay kharab aur is ke izzat walon ko zaleel kar dete hain yahi kuch woh kya karte hain"
  27,35,"mein inn logon ki taraf aik Hadia bhijti hon, phir dekhatii hon ke mere alchi kya jawab le kar palatne hain """
  27,36,"jab woh ( malka ka safeer ) sulaiman ke haan pouncha to is ne kaha"" kya tum log maal se meri madad karna chahtay ho? jo kuch khuda ne mujhe day rakha hai woh is se bohat ziyada hai jo tumhe diya hai tumhara Hadia tumhi ko mubarak rahay"
  27,37,"( ae safeer ) wapas ja apne bhejnay walon ki taraf hum un par aisay lashkar le kar ayen ge jin ka muqaabla woh nah kar saken ge aur hum inhen aisi zillat ke sath wahan se nikalen ge ke woh khawar ho kar reh jayen ge """
  27,38,"sulaiman ne kaha"" “اay ahal darbaar, tum mein se kon is ka takhat mere paas lata hai qabal is ke ke woh log Mutee ho kar mere paas haazir hon? """
  27,39,"junoo mein se aik quwwat hekal ne arz kya"" mein usay haazir kar dun ga qabal is ke ke aap apni jagah se utheen mein is ki taaqat rakhta hon aur amanatdar hon """
  27,40,"jis shakhs ke paas kitaab ka ilm tha woh bola"" mein aap ki palak jhapkane se pehlay usay laaye deta hon"" jounhi ke sulaiman ne woh takhat apne paas rakha howa dekha, woh pukaar utha"" yeh mere rab ka fazl hai taakay woh mujhe aazamaa_e ke mein shukar karta hon ya kafir Nemat ban jata hon aur jo koi shukar karta hai is ka shukar is ke apne hi liye mufeed hai, warna koi nashukri kere to mera rab be niaz aur apni zaat mein aap buzurag hai """
  27,41,"sulaiman ne kaha"" anjaan tareeqay se is ka takhat is ke samnay rakh do, dekhen woh sahih baat taq pahunchti hai ya unn logon mein se hai jo raah e raast nahi paate """
  27,42,"malka jab haazir hui to is se kaha gaya kya tera takhat aisa hi hai? woh kehnay lagi"" yeh to goya wohi hai hum to pehlay hi jaan gay thay aur hum ne sar-e itaat jhuka diya tha ( ya hum muslim ho chuke thay ) """
  27,43,"uss ko ( imaan laane se ) jis cheez ne rok rakha tha woh unn mabodon ki ibadat thi jinhein woh Allah ke siwa پوجتی thi, kyunkay woh aik kafir qoum se thi"
  27,44,"is se kaha gaya ke mehal mein daakhil ho is ne jo dekha to samjhi ke pani ka hoz hai aur utrney ke liye is ne apne painchay utha liye sulaiman ne kaha yeh sheeshay ka chikna farsh hai is par woh pukaar uthi"" ae mere rab, ( aaj taq ) mein apne nafs par bara zulm karti rahi, aur ab mein ne sulaiman ke sath Allah rab alameen ki itaat qubool kar li """
  27,45,"aur smod ki taraf hum ne unn ke bhai Saleh ko ( yeh pegham day kar ) bheja ke Allah ki bandagi karo, to yakayak woh do mutakhasim fareeq (jhagarnay walay) ban gay"
  27,46,"saleh ne kaha"" “ay meri qoum ke logo, bhalai se pehlay buraii ke liye kyun jaldi machate ho? kyun nahi Allah se mughfirat talab karte? shayad ke tum par reham farmaya jaye? """
  27,47,"unhon ne kaha"" hum ne to tum ko aur tumahray sathiyon ko bad shugooni ka nishaan paaya hai"" saleh ne jawab diya"" “tumharay naik o bad shagoon ka sir rishta to Allah ke paas hai asal baat yeh hai ke tum logon ki azmaish ho rahi hai """
  27,48,uss shehar mein no jithay daar thay jo malik mein fasaad pheilatay aur koi islaah ka kaam nah karte thay
  27,49,"unhon ne aapas mein kaha"" khuda ki qasam kha kar ehad kar lau ke hum saleh aur is ke ghar walon par shab khoon marain ge aur phir is ke walii se keh den ge ke hum is khandan ki halakat ke mauqa par mojood nah thay, hum bilkul sach kehte hain """
  27,50,yeh chaal to woh chalay aur phir aik chaal hum ne chali jis ki inhen khabar nah thi
  27,51,ab dekh lau ke un ki chaal ka injaam kya howa hum ne tabah kar ke rakh diya unn ko aur un ki poori qoum ko
  27,52,"woh unn ke ghar khaali parre hain uss zulm ki Padaash mein jo woh karte thay, is mein aik nishaan Ibrat hai unn logon ke liye jo ilm rakhtay hain"
  27,53,aur bacha liya hum ne unn logon ko jo imaan laaye thay aur nafarmani se parhaiz karte thay
  27,54,"aur loot ko hum ne bheja yaad karo woh waqt jab is ne apni qoum se kaha"" kya tum aankhon dekhte badkaari karte ho ?"
  27,55,"kya tumhara yahi chalan hai ke aurton ko chore kar mardon ke paas shehwat rani ke liye jatay ho? haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum log sakht jahalat ka kaam karte ho """
  27,56,"magar uss ki qoum ka jawab is ke siwa kuch nah tha ke unhon ne kaha"" nikaal do loot ke ghar walon ko apni bastii se, yeh barray pakbaaz bantay hain """
  27,57,"aakhir-kaar hum ne bacha liya uss ko aur uss ke ghar walon ko, bajuz uss ki biwi ke jis ka peechay reh jana hum ne tey kar diya tha"
  27,58,"aur brsayi unn logon par aik barsaat, bohat hi buri barsaat thi woh unn logon ke haq mein jo mutnabba kiye ja chuke thay"
  27,59,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) kaho, hamd Allah ke liye aur salam is ke unn bundon par jinhein is ne bargzida kya ( inn se pucho ) Allah behtar hai ya woh mabood jinhein yeh log is ka shareek bana rahay hain ?"
  27,60,"bhala woh kon hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko peda kya aur tumahray liye aasman se pani barsaya phir is ke zareya se woh khushnuma baagh ugaye jin ke darakhton ka ugana tumahray bas mein nah tha? kya Allah ke sath koi dosra khuda bhi ( inn kamon mein shareek ) hai? ( nahi ), balkay yahi log raah e raast se hatt kar chalay ja rahay hain"
  27,61,"aur woh kon hai jis ne zameen ko jaye qarar banaya aur is ke andar darya rawan kiye aur is mein ( pahoron ki ) maikhain garh den aur pani ke do zkhiron ke darmain parday haail kar diye? kya Allah ke sath koi aur khuda bhi ( inn kamon mein shareek ) hai? nahi, balkay inn mein se aksar log nadaan hain"
  27,62,kon hai jo be qarar ki dua santa hai jabkay woh ussay pukare aur kon is ki takleef rafa karta hai? aur ( kon hai jo ) tumhe zameen ka khalifa banata hai? kya Allah ke sath koi aur khuda bhi ( yeh kaam karne wala ) hai? tum log kam hi sochte ho
  27,63,aur woh kon hai jo khushki aur samandar ki tarikeon mein tum ko rasta dekhata hai aur kon apni rehmat ke agay hawaon ko khushkhabri le kar bhejta hai? kya Allah ke sath koi dُosra khuda bhi ( yeh kaam karta ) hai? bohat baala o bartar hai Allah is shirk se jo yeh log karte hain
  27,64,aur kon hai jo Khalq ki ibtida karta aur phir is ka iada karta hai? aur kon tum ko aasman aur zameen se rizaq deta hai? kya Allah ke sath koi aur khuda bhi ( inn kamon mein hissa daar ) hai? kaho ke lao apni Daleel agar tum sachey ho
  27,65,"inn se kaho, Allah ke siwa asmano aur zameen mein koi ghaib ka ilm nahi rakhta, aur woh nahi jantay ke kab woh uthaye jayen ge"
  27,66,"balkay akhirat ka to ilm hi inn logon se gum ho gaya hai, balkay yeh is ki taraf se shak mein hain, balkay yeh uss se andhay hain"
  27,67,"yeh munkareen kehte hain"" kya jab hum aur hamaray baap dada matti ho chuke hon ge to hamein waqai qabron se nikala jaye ga ?"
  27,68,"yeh khabrain hum ko bhi bohat di gayi hain aur pehlay hamaray aaba ajdaad ko bhi di jati rahi hain, magar yeh bas afsaanay hi afsaanay hain jo aglay waqton se suntay chalay aa rahay hain """
  27,69,kaho zara zameen mein chal phir kar dekho ke mujrimon ka kya injaam ho chuka hai
  27,70,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn ke haal par ranj nah karo aur nah inn ki chalon par dil tang ho"
  27,71,"woh kehte hain ke"" yeh dhamki kab poori ho gi agar tum sachey ho? """
  27,72,kaho kya ajab ke jis azaab ke liye tum jaldi macha rahay ho is ka aik hissa tumahray qareeb hi aa laga ho
  27,73,haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab to logon par bara fazl frmane wala hai magar aksar log shukar nahi karte
  27,74,bulaa shuba tera rab khob jaanta hai jo kuch un ke seenay apne andar chupaye hue hain aur jo kuch woh zahir karte hain
  27,75,aasman o zameen ki koi posheeda cheez aisi nahi hai jo aik wazeh kitaab mein likhi hui mojood nah ho
  27,76,yeh waqea hai ke yeh quran bani Israel ko aksar unn baton ki haqeeqat batata hai jin mein woh ikhtilaaf rakhtay hain
  27,77,aur yeh hadaayat aur rehmat hai imaan laane walon ke liye
  27,78,yaqeenan ( isi terhan ) tera rab inn logon ke darmain bhi apne hukum se faisla kar day ga aur woh zabardast aur sab kuch jan-nay wala hai
  27,79,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, Allah par bhrosa rakho, yaqeenan tum Sarih haq par ho"
  27,80,"tum mُrdon ko nahi suna satke, nah unn behroon taq apni pukaar pouncha satke ho jo peeth phair kar bhage ja rahay hon"
  27,81,aur nah andhon ko rasta bta kar bhatakne se bacha satke ho tum to apni baat aُnhi logon ko suna satke ho jo hamari ayaat par imaan laatay hain aur phir farmaan bardaar ban jatay hain
  27,82,aur jab hamari baat poori honay ka waqt unn par aa puhanche ga to hum un ke liye aik janwar zameen se nikalen ge jo un se kalaam kere ga ke log hamari ayaat par yaqeen nahi karte thay
  27,83,"aur zara tasawwur karo uss din ka jab hum har ammt mein se aik fouj ki fouj unn logon ki ghair layein ge jo hamari ayaat ko jhatlaya karte thay, phir un ko ( un ki aqsam ke lehaaz se darja badarja ) muratab kya jaye ga"
  27,84,"yahan taq ke jab sab aa jayen ge to ( un ka rab un se ) pouchye ga ke"" tum ne meri ayaat ko jhutla diya halaank tum ne un ka Ilmi ihata nah kya tha? agar yeh nahi to aur tum kya kar rahay thay? """
  27,85,"aur un ke zulm ki wajah se azaab ka wada un par poora ho jaye ga, tab woh kuch bhi nah bol saken ge"
  27,86,kya un ko sujhai nah deta tha ke hum ne raat un ke liye sukoon haasil karne ko banai thi aur din ko roshan kya tha? isi mein bohat nishanain theen un logon ke liye jo imaan laatay thay
  27,87,"aur kya guzray gi is roz jab ke soor phonka jaye ga aur houlle kha jayen ge woh sab jo asmano aur zameen mein hain, siwaye unn logon ke jinhein Allah is houlle se bachana chahay ga, aur sab kaan dabay is ke huzoor haazir ho jayen ge"
  27,88,"aaj to pahoron ko daikhta hai aur samjhta hai ke khoob jamay hue hain, magar uss waqt yeh baadalon ki terhan urr rahay hon ge, yeh Allah ki qudrat ka karishma ho ga jis ne har cheez ko hikmat ke sath ustuwar kya hai woh khoob jaanta hai ke tum log kya karte ho"
  27,89,jo shakhs bhalai le kar aayega usay uss se ziyada behtar sila miley ga aur aisay log uss din ke houlle se mehfooz hon ge
  27,90,"aur jo buraii liye hue aeye ga, aisay sab log avndhe mun aag mein phainky jayen ge kya tum log is ke siwa koi aur jaza pa satke ho ke jaissa karo waisa bharo ?"
  27,91,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho )"" mujhe to yahi hukum diya gaya hai ke iss shehar ke rab ki bandagi karoon jis ne isay haram banaya hai aur jo har cheez ka maalik hai mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke mein muslim ban kar rahon"
  27,92,"aur yeh quran parh kar sunaoon"" ab jo hadaayat ikhtiyar kere ga woh apne hi bhallay ke liye hadaayat ikhtiyar kere ga aur jo gumraah ho uss se keh do ke mein to bas khabardaar kar dainay wala hon"
  27,93,"inn se kaho, tareef Allah hi ke liye hai, anqareeb woh tumhe apni nishanain dikha day ga aur tum inhen pehchan lau ge, aur tera rab be khabar nahi hai unn aamaal se jo tum log karte ho"
